## Agreement

Running [this recipe](tagCmp.tgz) in CMSSW_7_4_0_pre7 I get:

Payload               | Agrees for
----------------------|-----------------
L1GtTriggerMenu       | Always disagree
L1GctJetFinderParams  | >= 2012 C
L1MuDTTFParameters    | >= 2012 C
L1MuCSCPtLut          | >= 2012 B
L1JetEtScale          | >= 2011 Cosmics
L1HtMissScale         | >= 2011 Cosmics 
L1HfRingEtScale       | >= 2011 Cosmics
